{
  "stem": "15686.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's simply an acronym.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The letters O-S-E, with an accent on the e.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In French, it's pronounced 'oh-zay.' It stands for Oeuvre de Secours aux Enfants, which means simply organization to help children.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had no idea who was funding them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we knew, or we were told that they had a network of children's homes in unoccupied France.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that there were French Jewish children there, and also some German refugee and Austrian refugee children there in these homes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now the home we landed in Limoges was really a home geared to small children-- babies, toddlers and kids of that age.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were a little too big by this time, my brother and I.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So after about three weeks there, they sent us to another home, which was about 100 miles or so north of Limoges but still in unoccupied France, in a department called Creuse.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the little-- tiny little village of about 100 people, was called Chabannes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this big country house that this home was in now was called the Chateau de Chabannes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It wasn't really a chateau.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was just a nice old country house, sort of Georgian style.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
